            <thetext>This problem isn&#39;t limited to qxDragAndDropToObject, it occurs whenever the qooxdoo Selenium extension&#39;s triggerMouseEventQx method tries to fire a synthetic DOM event on the &quot;dragHandle&quot; child element of one of the portal&#39;s content boxes. Triggering events on the parent DIV element works fine, however.</thetext>
